race.comment: MARGOT'S DEEL (16) goes well for rider Graham who has a win and two placings from just three steers and gets in on the minimum weight here. Racing very consistently this time in work and should be right there when the judge calls a halt. RHUVAAL (4) was a touch plain at the latest effort but go on the strong Doomben victory two back. Can bounce right back without shocking. THINKHARDANDFAST (15) has only missed a drum once in nine career outings and doesn't know how to run a bad race. A must for the multiples. PERFECT PLAY (3) has won two from four over this mile journey and will be ready to peak now fourth-up from the break. Genuine top-three candidate. PHENOM (13) next in line from the favourable draw.
